{"id":639694,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/直面传媒-今天，汉口殡仪馆排了很长的队伍：没/","date":"2020-03-26T19:54:52Z","modified":"2020-03-26T19:54:52Z","title":"直面传媒 | 今天，汉口殡仪馆排了很长的队伍：没有哭声，也没有哀乐！","content":"<p>原创：直面传媒</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>天气预报说：今天的武汉，阴天有小雨。然而，与乌云遮蔽的天空相比，更令人沉重的是排在汉口殡仪馆长长的队伍。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_639699\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-639699\" class=\"wp-image-639699\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/IMG_5585-165x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"909\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/IMG_5585-165x300.jpg 165w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/IMG_5585-563x1024.jpg 563w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/IMG_5585-768x1396.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/IMG_5585-845x1536.jpg 845w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/IMG_5585.jpg 1054w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-639699\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">CDT编者配图</p></div>\n<p>毛大庆在较早前发了一条消息说：武汉殡仪馆门口，排满了领取骨灰盒的人。</p>\n<p>但很快，图片就404了。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_639700\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-639700\" class=\"wp-image-639700\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/IMG_5586-138x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1085\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/IMG_5586-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/IMG_5586-472x1024.jpg 472w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/IMG_5586.jpg 590w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-639700\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">CDT编者配图</p></div>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-639702\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/b111544416fa416bab8e17db012036c4-300x90.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"149\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/b111544416fa416bab8e17db012036c4-300x90.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/b111544416fa416bab8e17db012036c4-768x229.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/b111544416fa416bab8e17db012036c4.jpeg 931w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>一位武汉的小姑娘说：为什么有人发了汉口殡仪馆排队的图片，却被删被限流？我经历了整个领取过程，社区提前预约了，早上8点到殡仪馆排队4个小时。有多少亲属们的悲伤，愤慨，却只有认命。多少个没有被确诊的人，最后就成了一个冰冷的盒子？数字之外的他们都被忘了吗？都不值得一提吗？</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-639701\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/728a47242fa04b6d991b050a0d53f306-300x170.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/728a47242fa04b6d991b050a0d53f306-300x170.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/728a47242fa04b6d991b050a0d53f306.jpeg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>一直到19分钟前，广东省共青团官微转发了微博。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-639698\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/cfc3219617be4d79b5bb2b5b51b420af-300x205.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"341\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/cfc3219617be4d79b5bb2b5b51b420af-300x205.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/cfc3219617be4d79b5bb2b5b51b420af.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-639696\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/83ddb5e7bcf44347a4eabbad68c95a52-300x228.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"380\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/83ddb5e7bcf44347a4eabbad68c95a52-300x228.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/83ddb5e7bcf44347a4eabbad68c95a52.jpeg 503w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>今天，武汉汉口殡仪馆外，领取骨灰的亲属们排起了长队……队伍静静的，反倒让人揪心、想哭!</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-639695\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/0d582844d33b4ce788816dfedaed332f-300x196.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/0d582844d33b4ce788816dfedaed332f-300x196.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/0d582844d33b4ce788816dfedaed332f.jpeg 598w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>之后，共青团昆明市委也转发了&#8230;&#8230;.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-639697\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/76189ba8e5bd4da0bd5b8c38ca0b0cfc-300x173.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"288\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/76189ba8e5bd4da0bd5b8c38ca0b0cfc-300x173.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/76189ba8e5bd4da0bd5b8c38ca0b0cfc.jpeg 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>一位前往殡仪馆的网友说：我是今天上午10点左右到汉口殡仪馆的，大门口沿路停着长长的私家车和志愿者车队，进门安保很严&#8230;..基本一抬手机就有人过来制止。我在里面待了两个小时，有的家属抱着遗照坐在对接点等待，有的抱着骨灰盒从我身边走过。</p>\n<p>他说：人很多，很安静，没有哭声，也没有哀乐，他们就这样默默地抱着骨灰盒离开。只到最后我要离开才看到一位阿姨放声大哭，她的哭声引来所有人回头，大家呆呆地看着她，甚至有一丝尴尬。</p>\n<p>这次灾难，似乎已让很多人痛到失去了知觉。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[18271,38827,38912,39924,39707],"tags":[40076,40078,39788]}